1. *Učio* sam matematiku sinoć. (I studied math last night.)
2. On *uči* engleski jezik već tri godine. (He has been studying English for three years.)
3. Kada *učiš* za ispit? (When are you studying for the exam?)
4. Moja sestra *uči* da svira klavir. (My sister is learning to play the piano.)
5. Da li si *učio* istoriju u srednjoj školi? (Did you study history in high school?)
6. *Učenje* stranih jezika može biti korisno za karijeru. (Learning foreign languages can be beneficial for your career.)
7. Nikada ne prestajte *učiti* i usavršavati se. (Never stop learning and improving yourself.)
8. *Učenik* je dobio pet za matematiku. (The student got an A in math.) 
9. Njegov otac ga *uči* kako da vozi auto. (His father is teaching him how to drive a car.)
10. Oni *uče* u biblioteci svakog dana. (They study in the library every day.)